<p>One &#8220;evil&#8221; thing is the deployment of DRM on videos; first on Google Video some years ago, now on premium YouTube video; and also in the Android platform. There&#8217;s no customer case for this &#8212; it&#8217;s purely about increasing revenue while making things worse for customers.</p>

